, 
<materialsCitation ID-GBIF-Occurrence="3818814655" pageId="81" pageNumber="360">San Luis Potosi, San Luis Potosi, Mexico. N.</materialsCitation>
<taxonomicName authorityName="Merriam" authorityYear="1894" box="[217,326,3287,3320]" class="Mammalia" family="Cricetidae" genus="Neotoma" kingdom="Animalia" order="Rodentia" pageId="81" pageNumber="360" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="leucodon">leucodon</taxonomicName>
was removed as a subspecies of N. 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Hartley" authorityYear="1894" box="[826,928,3287,3320]" class="Mammalia" family="Cricetidae" genus="Neotoma" kingdom="Animalia" order="Rodentia" pageId="81" pageNumber="360" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="albigula">albigula</taxonomicName>
